appreciates its monumental achievements since the introduction of
reform and opening some two decades ago.
</P>
<P>
Belarus will promote the continuous development of bilateral
friendship and cooperation between the two countries, according to
the foreign minister. He also praised Hong Kong's achievements
since its return to the motherland one year ago.
</P>
<P>
Antonovich briefed Hu on the domestic situation in his country,
as well as its domestic and foreign policies. He noted that
Belarus has scored great successes in national economic
development since gaining independence and will continue current
policies and extend great effort to safeguard its independence and
promote economic development.
</P>
<P>
Hu thanked Antonovich for his invitation to visit Belarus.
