<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Turkish Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANAKRA, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading Turkish newspapers Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Sabah (Morning):
</P>
<P>
-- Turkish Prime Minister Mesut Yilmaz said Tuesday that the
agreement signed by Turkey and the International Monetary
Agreement (IMF) last week in Washington would affect Turkish
economy "very positively".
</P>
<P>
