<HEADLINE> President Clinton Visits Bourse, Family in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, July 1 (Xinhua) -- Visiting U.S. President Bill
Clinton arrived at Jinhui Gardens, a housing development project
