<HEADLINE> Maradona Praises Argentine Team's Win in Second Round </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, June 30 (Xinhua) -- Argentine soccer star Diego
Maradona Tuesday praised his country's second round World Cup
victory over England for a 4-3 win on penalties.
</P>
<P>
He said: "They (England) changed the old style of playing
through the centers for a passing game. But the Argentine boys
fought like lions and gave us this joy."
