<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Pakistani Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading Pakistani English newspapers on Wednesday.
</P>
