</P>
<P>
-- Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif on Tuesday announced revival of
all foreign exchange accounts, saying a notification to this
effect will be issued by State Bank of Pakistan shortly.
</P>
<P>
The Nation:
</P>
<P>
