<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, June 30 (Xinhua) -- President of the General
Assembly of the United Nations Hennadiy Udovenko Tuesday expressed
his condolences on the death of Angola Envoy and his colleagues in
an air crash Friday.
</P>
<P>
In a statement, Udovenko said he was profoundly saddened to
learn about the tragic death in an aircraft accident of Blondin
Beye, the secretary-general's special envoy for Angola, and five
